#: library/turtle.rst:2343
msgid ""
"The first four lines correspond to the arguments of the :meth:`Screen.setup` "
"method."
msgstr ""
"Les quatre premières lignes correspondent aux arguments de la méthode :meth:"
"`Screen.setup`."

#: library/turtle.rst:2345
